islike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T22:00:09.000Z","msg":"德國讀碩士 你覺得你需要幾多年先畢到業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8b75383550ec7c8213511df7a8041ccf0a79d97","tid":459529,"uid":55327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T23:39:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1302ce8eca91891bcabdf8d50ff387c2100f78eb","tid":459529,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T01:51:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打重有冇更新？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有。不日出文。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為係邊寫邊連載，所以唔未必出文出得好密<br />\n<br />\n但一定唔爛尾</blockquote><br />\nOk，慢慢嚟啦巴打"},{"pid":"2e0f04ad8a3043e98241f1b51b0efae200a8aebf","tid":459529,"uid":52294,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T05:00:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ac92cc503b370b745ee8882be68316869cb7bc55","tid":459529,"uid":130776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T14:13:10.000Z","msg":"英國jj留名, 有諗過去lmu/Heidelberg pg <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0a70e98db4f06e8686b357b63b2af44c73b830d","tid":459529,"uid":41243,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T15:40:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪一定要識德文</blockquote><br />\n老實講我見到嚟呢邊讀啲香港人十個有七個都唔識，反而大陸人識德文既比例仲高"},{"pid":"09cb53c8061b72c3a5aa37d68644d740850aeafa","tid":459529,"uid":74264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T15:44:00.000Z","msg":"留明"},{"pid":"1ecf5683044ec061c5e0e13dcbb36592f2e6fd57","tid":459529,"uid":41243,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T15:44:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係咪一定要識德文</blockquote><br />\n老實講我見到嚟呢邊讀啲香港人十個有七個都唔識，反而大陸人識德文既比例仲高</blockquote><br />\n雖然大陸人啲德文口音真係好撚難聽, 同香港NDS既英文口音如出一轍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁耐喺嗰邊只係見過兩至三個大陸人德文係堅掂<br />\n一個喺C2 course預到，喺本身大陸讀德文中學去到讀Deutsch als Fremdsprache (German as a foreign language)<br />\n一個係讀教育碩士<br />\n一個最癲，喺大陸讀完德文學士，去到由law bachelor讀起，再上law master，讀咗勁撚多年書 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申德文唔鹹唔淡，不過起碼德國人同我傾計未至於會唔耐煩想轉channel <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02bec41b223f3f0684023060b0491ec762b40a7c","tid":459529,"uid":29314,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T14:33:37.000Z","msg":"【80後出走德國去讀書系列】<br />\n<br />\n第二回：行之有效既垃圾分類<br />\n<br />\n一、係德國,每個家庭都會做垃圾分類,（並非強制性，但人地細細個學校就教環保有幾重要。早係九十年代，德國人出街已經自備購物袋，又會自發做垃圾分類。）唔似得香港咁將所有垃圾都放埋一齊。<br />\n<br />\n德國的垃圾分類有紙張, 塑膠, 廚餘, 玻璃同埋其他。大廈會有唔同顏色的箱去放置垃圾, 紙張係藍色, 塑膠係黃色, 廚餘係啡或者綠色, 其他係黑色。<br />\n<br />\n二、另外係德國買膠樽或者玻璃飲品要額外比一種叫Einwegpfand (簡稱Pfand)的按金,目的係想大眾回收膠樽同玻璃。買膠樽或者玻璃飲品個陣要比多0.25歐(膠樽)或者0.08歐(玻璃),飲完之後大眾可以拎番去超市退回按金。<br />\n<br />\n（呢樣野係挪威都一樣有，仲擴展到飲品鋁罐。當地超級市場有部自動回收機，你放空樽、空罐入去，佢會自動scan個barcode，然後會印返相應金額既現金卷畀你係超市消費。千祈不要學香港的阿婆，走去踩扁鋁罐，部回收機掃不到barcode是不會退回按金。另外，不要嘗試帶洋垃圾到挪威變現，因barcode不同，回收機是會拒收來自香港的樽和罐。）<br />\n<br />\n反觀香港，垃圾分類完全依賴大量低下層在社區進行。在經濟誘因之下，有變賣價值的垃圾（例如紙張、金屬）才會被分揀出來再回收。沒變賣價值的垃圾，（例如膠、玻璃）因市民缺乏環保意識、又沒有政府主動介入，往往沒有人要而倒入堆填區。<br />\n<br />\n#移民 #出走 #德國<br />\n<br />\n（圖一：我屋企樓下的回收箱）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/223322_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F223322_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=0666d7ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖二：每買一支就要比0.25歐）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/223332_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F223332_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=a75f5354&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1703ec66a6341933ff1841851372b2a948ac7825","tid":459529,"uid":29314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T14:35:19.000Z","msg":"同步連載：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/WestRiceGoo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FWestRiceGoo&d=wdibREn%2B18OlSkWxh8ewn5zN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=bce3f6a6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/WestRiceGoo</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/westricegoo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fwestricegoo&d=wdibREn%2B18OlSkWxh8ewn5zN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=69f8ffb8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.instagram.com/westricegoo</a>"},{"pid":"f57fa236863ab1da94f71eb9c4603d528e157435","tid":459529,"uid":40216,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T15:13:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係咪一定要識德文</blockquote><br />\n老實講我見到嚟呢邊讀啲香港人十個有七個都唔識，反而大陸人識德文既比例仲高</blockquote><br />\n雖然大陸人啲德文口音真係好撚難聽, 同香港NDS既英文口音如出一轍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁耐喺嗰邊只係見過兩至三個大陸人德文係堅掂<br />\n一個喺C2 course預到，喺本身大陸讀德文中學去到讀Deutsch als Fremdsprache (German as a foreign language)<br />\n一個係讀教育碩士<br />\n一個最癲，喺大陸讀完德文學士，去到由law bachelor讀起，再上law master，讀咗勁撚多年書 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申德文唔鹹唔淡，不過起碼德國人同我傾計未至於會唔耐煩想轉channel <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n德國法學博士翻支那可以直接入研究院，所以支那好多法學教授都係德國/日本讀書"},{"pid":"109a6cc5322b8f6c506064624e87cf6f65c713a2","tid":459529,"uid":29314,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T23:48:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/16/074817_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F16%2F074817_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=730a0cab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n十一月的德國。室外氣溫4度。"},{"pid":"f2aedc76b78509a60e2b588ed5708e648e2baeb5","tid":45